sequenceDiagram
  participant S as Student
  participant UI as Learning Interface
  participant AC as Adaptive Controller
  participant AE as AI Engine

  S->>UI: Submit answer / interact with activity
  UI->>AC: processAnswer(questionData, isCorrect, userAnswer)
  Note over AC: Calculate response time<br/>from session start
  AC->>AE: analyzeResponse(questionData, isCorrect, responseTime, topic)
  Note over AE: Update performance metrics<br/>Update student profile<br/>Track learning patterns
  AC->>AE: adjustDifficulty()
  Note over AE: Analyze recent responses<br/>Apply adaptation rules<br/>Update difficulty level
  AC->>AC: generateFeedback(questionData, isCorrect, responseTime)
  AC-->>UI: {feedback, difficultyAdjustment, insights}
  UI->>UI: Update interface (feedback, progress indicators)
  Note over UI: Display personalized messages<br/>Update learning status
